Assignment 4

Category

AWS Resources
Terraform
Jenkins


Details
In this assignment, we will create an end-to-end infrastructure using Terraform resources.

Must Do

Take reference to your previously created architecture diagram and create terraform code to implement the complete infrastructure over AWS.
Make sure the code should be based on the principle of re-usability. Try to use vars and tfvars
All the required details should be part of the output information


Good to Do

Create a Jenkins automation pipeline to implement all the terraform phases i.e. validation, planning, and creation.


References

https://www.terraform.io/docs
